{
  "name": "Psychic Imbued",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/magic/fire/dagger-rune-enchant-flame-teal-purple.webp",
  "system": {
    "itemKey": "",
    "description": "<p>For the duration, you deal +1 Psychic damage on Martial Attacks.</p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Spell Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><p><strong>Range: (1 AP)</strong> The range becomes 5 Spaces, allowing you to target other creatures with the Spell.</p><p><strong>Damage: (2 MP, Repeatable)</strong> Your Attacks affected by this Spell deal +1 Psychic damage.</p><p><strong>Effortless: (1 MP)</strong> You no longer need to Sustain the Spell.</p><p><strong>Targets: (1 AP + X MP)</strong> You target X additional creatures of your choice within 5 Spaces that you can see. When you choose this Enhancement, the cost of all other Enhancements (except Range and Effortless) is doubled. The AP cost of this Enhancement can’t be paid for with MP (see Mana Points on AP Enhancements).</p><p><strong>Dazing Strikes: (1 MP)</strong> Once per round, 1 target of an Attack affected by this Spell makes an Intelligence Save against your Save DC. <strong>Save Failure:</strong> The target is Dazed for 1 round.</p><p><strong>Silencing Strikes: (1 MP)</strong> Once per round, 1 target of an Attack affected by this Spell makes a Charisma Save against your Save DC. <strong>Failure:</strong> The target is Deafened and can’t speak for 1 round.</p>",
